transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Ji haan, aap se baat ho rahi hai?
Customer: Ji boliye.
Executive: Bhai main bol raha hun main demo tak organize ho.
Executive: Achcha ji. Aaj mini khul pa raha hai wo aap bata rahe the batao.
Customer: Haan dusre call pe tha main. Sorry, abhi lunch mein call kiya maine. To basically kuch photos bheji thi Mohsin ji ne to wo maine add kar di thi. Mere ko na kuch product ke prices aapse janne the.
Executive: Achcha.
Customer: Right and abhi matlab do photos bhi chahiye garden waterfall ki. To ye mil jayega on call?
Executive: Dekhta hun ek second main.
Customer: Hmm. Aur mere ko garden waterfall ka koi ek rate bata sakte hain?
Executive: Mohsin bhai bataye nahi ki Mohsin bhai ne nahi bataya kya?
Customer: Nahi actually aap hi use kar rahe ho IndiaMART se maine aapko phone kar liya unko phone hi nahi kiya maine.
Executive: Wo wo better bata payenge.
Customer: Kya keh rahe hain?
Executive: Unse baat karni padegi.
Customer: Price wagera to unse baat kar lo ek baar to wo kya kehte hain.
Executive: Theek hai, ek baar unse baat karta hun main.
Executive: Theek hai, okay.
summary:

- Customer wants to know product prices.

- Customer needs two photos of garden waterfall.
